Author: CryptoInvestICO
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: ICO Analysis: MYDFS Published on April 25, 2018 By Aakash Kawale  Team In 2016, CEO Viktor Mangazeev founded uTrener.com (utrener.com), a daily mobile fantasy sports platform that launched in Russia. They also have a white label application which has been gaining traction. Having a white label app that is used to create fantasy sports applications shows the team’s expertise in this segment. There are 12 members of the team, all of them work full time on MyDFS. They have six advisers, which includes tech and crypto entrepreneurs and also one football player.  Token The Ethereum based MyDFS tokens will power the platform. The tokens will be used for game entry fees, reward distribution, advanced functions like p2p duels/access to leaderboards, in-game purchases, and sponsor integrations. The tokens have a good utility across the platform and, as the adoption grows, the demand for tokens will increase. Users interact with fantasy sports applications on a daily basis which will keep the demand consistent. The token distribution is as follows:     ICO Distribution: 40%     Growth and user adoption reserves: 37%     Team: 10%     Advisers and early contributors: 10%     Bounty: 3%  Verdict Fantasy sports was built out of a loophole in the law that normally bans such betting. It’s a growing industry, estimated to be worth more than $7 billion a year in the U.S. and Canada. MyDFS’s team has industry relevant experience which will help its cause in platform building and subsequent promotion. Blockchain technology finds a perfect use case in fantasy sports. Transparency and ease of payments is the most significant advantage in my opinion. Users located in different corners of the world can participate and earn from NBA matches, which is not possible without using the blockchain. A major area of concern is whether MyDFS will be able to gain market share in the key market of North America. Incumbents Fanduel and Draftkings are the undisputed leaders in the sector with a combined market share of 90% and have made it impossible for newer platforms to gain any share. It would be interesting to see whether the dual advantages of transparency and ease of payments are solid enough to enable a shift.  Growth Potential     One of the most tempting factors about MyDFS is that the platform will be fully functional by June 2018, before the FIFA World Cup. Very few projects have functional products immediately after the launch. Majority of the funds raised in the ICO will be used for marketing and promotional activities; the team doesn’t need as many funds for product development. +5     The team looks solid and already has a functional product serving the same use case without blockchain. +4     MyDFS opens a completely new market opportunity as it removes jurisdictional constraints using tokens and blockchain. Users located all over the world can participate and earn in any fantasy sports using MyDFS. +3  Risks     Competition is the biggest risk that MyDFS faces. Fanduel and Draftkings have raised a combined sum of more than $1 billion and have established a duopoly in the market. Other blockchain based projects like DraftDaily, Protoblock are vying to gain a share. -2     MyDFS is raising $40 million for 40% of the token supply, which makes the valuation based on total supply a bit steep for a company with no users. We are not sure whether MyDFS will achieve its targets. -2     Fantasy sports is a relatively new industry with just $7 Billion of total valuation. -1     Fantasy sports industry has primarily matured in North America and the U.K. However, US citizens are not allowed to participate in the ICO, thus losing an opportunity to distribute tokens amongst the primary audience. -1  Disposition We arrive at a score of +6 out of 10 for MyDFS. Although there are short-term concerns about the ability to reach its hard cap, MyDFS is a good project from a long-term investment perspective.  Proof: https://hacked.com/ico-analysis-mydfs/

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Hi! Let me please explain. 1. We are not starting from scratch, previously we’ve developed such successful apps as Utrener and KHL which fully function today and have a lot of followers in different countries 2. Our app is fully ready to be released in June right before FIFA 3. We work on the blockchain and smart contracts which means we are of full transparency. Unlike the Proprietary Backend, blockchain and smart contracts make all transaction transparent and safe to the core. Users can check all transaction history, in-game stats, other data at any time 4. We are fully integrated both with android/IOS and Web 5. We have a brand new feature - a brokerage platform. If you do not want to draft your own teams, you can invest money in professional players. Again, with a help of a brokerage contract, all the stats are available anytime on the blockchain. Your funds will not get lost or appropriated, as the smart contract will redirect all the processes without middlemen interference 6. Thanks to the smart contract again, all the transactions are processed almost instantly without any risks, delays and shadow economy 7. MyDFS token is a utility token which enables your rights to play games legally 8. We’ll charge a 10% rake only, still the lowest on the market  Please let me know if you have any questions left

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Hi! I can tell you about our advantages  1. We are not starting from scratch, previously we’ve developed such successful apps as Utrener and KHL which fully function today and have a lot of followers in different countries 2. Our app is fully ready to be released in June. If you want to be the first to get the use of it, please get whitelisted https://mydfs.net/referrals 3. We work on the blockchain and smart contracts which means we are of full transparency. Unlike the Proprietary Backend, blockchain and smart contracts make all transaction transparent and safe to the core. Users can check all transaction history, in-game stats, other data at any time 4. We are fully integrated both with android/IOS and Web 5. We have a brand new feature - a brokerage platform. If you do not want to draft your own teams, you can invest money in professional players. Again, with a help of a brokerage contract, all the stats are available anytime on the blockchain. Your funds will not get lost or appropriated, as the smart contract will redirect all the processes without middlemen interference 6. Thanks to the smart contract again, all the transactions are processed almost instantly without any risks, delays and shadow economy 7. MyDFS token is a utility token which enables your rights to play games legally 8. We’ll charge a 10% rake only, still the lowest on the market Finally, we appreciate our customers and are ready to solve your problems 24/7 in our TG channel so please join us and stay tuned!

Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Total supply of tokens will depend on the number of Purchased Tokens sold during Presale and ICO, plus Growth Tokens, Team Tokens, Advisors & early contributors tokens and Bounty program tokens allocated. Purchased Tokens — 40% of all tokens (50,000,000). The funds raised with Purchased Tokens will be used for business operations, product development, marketing and PR, and other milestones according to the project roadmap. Unsold tokens will be made non-transferrable, and removed from the usable supply. Growth Tokens — 37% of all tokens (46,250,000). Will be allocated timely to ensure proper user and affiliates incentives, and should help the project growth. Tokens issued for the growth pool will be used to incentivize a number of behaviors, like account verification, account deposits, completion of various in-game quests, sharing content on social networks, etc. Team Tokens — 10% of all tokens (12,500,000). Will be allocated to the members of MyDFS core team. Advisors tokens & early contributors — 10% of all tokens (12,500,000). Will be allocated to the advisors of MyDFS & early contributors. Bounty program — 3% of all tokens (3,750,000). Will be allocated for the bounty program.

Body: When fiat money is excluded from the process, it becomes significantly easier to expand to just about any country in the world. Most legal issues arise because the process of working with fiat money is usually complicated, requiring a lot of attention and verification. It’s also totally centralized, causing transaction delays and other problems. Tokens let people get value in and out of the system way faster, and with far fewer complications. For countries that require additional licensing, we will use a part of the project budget to obtain proper documents and licenses.

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Total supply of tokens will depend on the number of Purchased Tokens sold during Presale and ICO, plus Growth Tokens, Team Tokens, Advisors & early contributors tokens and Bounty program tokens allocated. Purchased Tokens — 40% of all tokens (50,000,000). The funds raised with Purchased Tokens will be used for business operations, product development, marketing and PR, and other milestones according to the project roadmap. Unsold tokens will be made non-transferrable, and removed from the usable supply. Growth Tokens — 37% of all tokens (46,250,000). Will be allocated timely to ensure proper user and affiliates incentives, and should help the project growth. Tokens issued for the growth pool will be used to incentivize a number of behaviors, like account verification, account deposits, completion of various in-game quests, sharing content on social networks, etc. Team Tokens — 10% of all tokens (12,500,000). Will be allocated to the members of MyDFS core team. Advisors tokens & early contributors — 10% of all tokens (12,500,000). Will be allocated to the advisors of MyDFS & early contributors. Bounty program — 3% of all tokens (3,750,000). Will be allocated for the bounty program.

Author: Vladdirescu87
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Creators of uTrener and KHL Fantasy Sport Apps Introduce Blockchain Powered Daily Fantasy Sports Platform MyDFS  A blockchain-powered daily fantasy sports platform, MyDFS promises to improve the gaming experience for uncountable amount of fantasy sports enthusiasts around the world by delivering better speed, ease-of-use, transparency, governance and accountability. This mobile based fantasy sports ecosystem has been created by the founders of uTrener and KHL Fantasy, two of European earliest and most popular daily fantasy sports platforms.  MyDFS is all set to redefine the industry by connecting the sports fans around the world to an ecosystem that is transparent, easy-to-use, and token buyers friendly. Built on smart contracts, MyDFS runs on mobile devices to address a number of issues that have plagued the fantasy sports industry. The ultimate goal of this project is to simplify the user experience to make the games enjoyable for all types of players.  Read the details in the article of Coinidol dot com, the world blockchain news outlet: https://coinidol.com/creators-of-utrener-introduce-mydfs/

Vesting applies to team tokens, ensuring that the team’s and advisors’ priorities properly align with the community’s. The team will successfully deliver the project as it’s stated in the project roadmap. Therefore, Advisor Tokens vest at 100% for 14 days after the close of the ICO sale. Founder and Core Team Tokens vest for one year from the date they are allocated. They are also unlocked by 1/12 each month. Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Our advantages: 1. We are not starting from scratch, previously we’ve developed such successful apps as Utrener and KHL which fully function today and have a lot of followers in different countries 2. Our app is fully ready to be released in May. If you want to be the first to get the use of it, please get whitelisted https://mydfs.net/referrals 3. We work on the blockchain and smart contracts which means we are of full transparency. Unlike the Proprietary Backend, blockchain and smart contracts make all transaction transparent and safe to the core. Users can check all transaction history, in-game stats, other data at any time 4. We are fully integrated both with android/IOS and Web 5. We have a brand new feature - a brokerage platform. If you do not want to draft your own teams, you can invest money in professional players. Again, with a help of a brokerage contract, all the stats are available anytime on the blockchain. Your funds will not get lost or appropriated, as the smart contract will redirect all the processes without middlemen interference 6. Thanks to the smart contract again, all the transactions are processed almost instantly without any risks, delays and shadow economy 7. MyDFS token is a utility token which enables your rights to play games legally 8. We’ve got the UK Gambling Commission License which is a very prestigious one by the way 9. We’ll charge a 10% rake only, still the lowest on the market 10. Finally, we appreciate our customers and are ready to solve your problems 24/7 🙂

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Player transactions happen almost instantly, and they aren’t charged any additional fees for it because there are no middlemen in the process. Transaction integrity is also guaranteed by using the blockchain, as every player has access to a full, anonymized transaction history. In case of any problems, it’s easy to find the source and fix the problem. It’s also convenient for investors. They get to monitor performance of the players they’ve invested in in realtime, get their winnings, and so on.

Author: Malonis
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Is it legal?

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Yes. When fiat money is excluded from the process, it becomes significantly easier to expand to just about any country in the world. Most legal issues arise because the process of working with fiat money is usually complicated, requiring a lot of attention and verification. It’s also totally centralized, causing transaction delays and other problems. Tokens let people get value in and out of the system way faster, and with far fewer complications. For countries that require additional licensing, we will use a part of the project budget to obtain proper documents and licences.

Body: Before starting the work on MyDFS, we've successfullly developed and launched a number of fantasy sport products, including: uTrener - one of the frirst platforms on the Russian market that offered a refines, user-friendly DFS gaming; White-label solution for KHL - an app for KHL, the top ice hockey league in Eastern Europe.

Author: Nige
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: What are you advantages over draftkings and fanduel?

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: We do not intend to compete with the major companies on the DFS market, we want to create new way to play dfs and change the industry. Fanduel and Draftkings haven’t implemented blockchain yet, so we are the pioneering the technology. Our team has wide experience in DFS industry. Two years ago we successfully released Utrener and KHL Fantasy apps, both projects are very popular in Russia and Western Europe.

Author: Maverin
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: What includes the sign up process?

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Users sign up with their existing Ethereum wallets, which we’ll link their game tokens to via QR-code, or by entering the address of their wallet, and then going through the wallet authentication procedure. The sign-in process stores authentication data locally so users don’t have to repeat the procedure every time they open the app.

Our app will be available ahead of the 2018 World Cup this summer in Russia, one of the world’s biggest sports events, which will be a great way to attract new fans and users and create a memorable experience.

Author: Cordalune
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Do you have any game entry fees?

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Yes. When a player participates in a game, he or she has to pay an entry fee. The total collected fee is distributed among the winners. We take a 10% rake from this total. The more contests and players are there on the platform, the more we earn. Existing fantasy sports platforms tend to take higher rake fees (up to 15%), which we are also going to challenge. We’ll also be charging smaller rake amounts for games with higher stakes.

Author: Dianameena
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: How are tokens distributed?

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: Total supply of tokens will depend on the number of Purchased Tokens sold during Presale and ICO, plus Growth Tokens, Team Tokens, Advisors & early contributors tokens and Bounty program tokens allocated. Purchased Tokens — 40% of all tokens (50,000,000). The funds raised with Purchased Tokens will be used for business operations, product development, marketing and PR, and other milestones according to the project roadmap. Unsold tokens will be made non-transferrable, and removed from the usable supply. Growth Tokens — 37% of all tokens (46,250,000). Will be allocated timely to ensure proper user and affiliates incentives, and should help the project growth. Tokens issued for the growth pool will be used to incentivize a number of behaviours, like account verification, account deposits, completion of various in-game quests, sharing content on social networks, etc. Team Tokens — 10% of all tokens (12,500,000). Will be allocated to the members of MyDFS core team. Advisors tokens & early contributors — 10% of all tokens (12,500,000). Will be allocated to the advisors of MyDFS & early contributors. Bounty program — 3% of all tokens (3,750,000). Will be allocated for the bounty program.

Body: The lockup period ensures that tokenholders don’t sell until 14 days after the last round of token sales is complete. After that, the tokens will be listed on a number of well-known, trustworthy exchanges. Vesting applies to team tokens, ensuring that the team’s and advisors’ priorities properly align with the community’s. The team will successfully deliver the project as it’s stated in the project roadmap. Therefore, Advisor Tokens vest at 100% for 14 days after the close of the ICO sale. Founder and Core Team Tokens vest for one year from the date they are allocated. They are also unlocked by 1/12 each month.

Author: Ocakypa
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🏈 MyDFS 🏀 - Platform solves a number of major issues faced by DFS
Body: _______________________________________________________________________________ ___________________________ Blockchain meets fantasy sports _______________________________________________________________________________ ___________________________   ####################  Read the MyDFS White Paper  ####################    ***********************************  Calm Down & Request a quote  ***********************************  TOKEN TYPE: HARD CAP: Utility token $40,000,000 PRE-SALE: ICO SALE: April 16 – May 6, 2018 June 11 – July 10, 2018 BASIC TOKEN PRICE: 1 MyDFS token = $1.00              ___________________________________________________________________________  We’re a team of industry pros with vast expertise in the fields of fantasy sports and large-audience applications.  We have successfully launched a number of fantasy products, including: — uTrener (utrener.com), one of the first DFS mobile platforms in Russia, recieveing its UK Gambling Commission license in 2017. — A white-label solution for KHL (fantasy.khl.ru) — a full-featured fantasy for the top ice hockey league in Eastern Europe, featured by Apple in the App Store. The reference from KHL is available here .   What is daily fantasy sport (DFS)? ___________________________________________________________________________  In the popular conception of fantasy sports, players draft a team and maintain it throughout an entire season, earning points when their players take effective action in real-world games. In daily fantasy sports, this whole season is reduced to one day. You’ll draft players in the morning and know your standing by the evening. Winners share the prize pool.    FANTASY SPORTS MARKET ___________________________________________________________________________  The fantasy sports market is one of explosive development, growing almost five times over the past ten years. With some 12.6 million players active in 2005, that number approached 60 million in 2017, just for the US and Canada alone. As of June 2017, the fantasy sports industry has a market capitalization exceeding $7 billion, with the average player spending of $556 per year. The market is dominated by a pair of companies, FanDuel and DraftKings, that together own almost 90% of the market. They are followed by smaller players like Yahoo Fantasy.    WHAT WE OFFER ___________________________________________________________________________  We solve existing fantasy sports problems using the blockchain and modern business practices. MyDFS offers:  Truly legal gaming around the world Our platform replaces fiat money with cryptocurrency tokens, instantly doing away with the legal issues usually associated with fantasy sports. MyDFS is accessible, enjoyable, and legal for everyone in the world.  A streamlined user experience Our simplified user interface suits any kind of gamer and challenges our competitors’ complex user experiences.  Fast user verification and worry-free transactions All it takes to get authorized on MyDFS and start collecting winnings is an email address and the cryptocurrency you receive upon signup. Smart contracts exclude middlemen from the entire transaction process, so every transaction on the platform is quickly executed and properly verified.  Transparent gaming and fair play Every transaction on our platform takes place on the blockchain, meaning they can be easily monitored by anyone involved (or even interested).  Profitable, investor-friendly gaming In addition to playing on the platform themselves, users can also invest in other fantasy players and share the winnings when they do well. Investor money can only be used for playing the games the competitor agreed to participate in.     BUDGET ALLOCATION ___________________________________________________________________________  55% Marketing & PR Digital marketing, social network promotion, offline marketing, and any operations to acquire users and promote the platform 18% Business Operations Support and business services, infrastructure costs 13% Development Salaries for the core development team, and other product development costs 8% Licensing and legal fees Compliance costs, content licensing costs, and sports data 6% Other costs A “rainy day” fund to be used for unanticipated expenses   MyDFS Token ___________________________________________________________________________  125,000,000   There will be 125 mln MyDFS tokens in total.  PURCHASED TOKENS 40% of all tokens (50,000,000) The funds raised with Purchased Tokens will be used for business operations, product development, marketing and PR, and other roadmap milestones. Unsold tokens will be made non-transferrable, and will be removed from the usable supply. GROWTH TOKENS 37% of all tokens (46,250,000) These will be allocated in a timely fashion to ensure proper incentives for users and affiliates, and should help the proj- ect’s growth. Tokens issued for the growth pool will be used to incentivize a number of behaviours, including account ver- ification, account deposits, completion of various in-game quests, sharing content on social networks, and so on. TEAM TOKENS 10% of all tokens (12,500,000) These will be allocated to the members of MyDFS core team. ADVISORS AND EARLY CONTRIBUTORS TOKENS 10% of all tokens (12,500,000) These will be allocated to the early contributors and advisory board . BOUNTY TOKENS 3% of all tokens (3,750,000) These will be allocated to the people supporting MyDFS and completing bounty tasks.    FACEBOOK •   TELEGRAM •     TWITTER •     MEDIUM    _______________  Bounty program LIVE _______________  MyDFS.net
